==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Zeuzerian
<hw>Zeu*ze"ri*an</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Zool.)</fld>
<def>Any one of a group of bombycid moths of which the genus
<gen>Zeuzera</gen> is the type. Some of these moths are of large size.
The goat moth is an example.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Zeylanite</ent>⟦br⟧
